                    <li>Updated Requests to 2.26.0</li>
                    <li>Updated Rx to 3.2.0</li>
                    <li>Updated Flatpak Gnome runtime to 40(3.40)</li>
                    <li>Updated Flatpak shared-modules</li>
                    <li>Updated Flatpak-builder-tools</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release date="2021-07-11" version="1.1.6">
