                    <li>Improved text of UDEV rules dialogs</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release date="2020-05-17" version="0.14.2">
            <description>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added dialog suggesting possible fix for UDEV rules</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release date="2020-04-09" version="0.14.1">
            <description>
                <ul>
                    <li>Updated dependencies</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release date="2019-09-29" version="0.14.0">
            <description>
                <ul>
                    <li>Updated several dependencies, including liquidctl 1.3.3</li>
