                    <li>Added warning dialog for legacy firmware 2.x</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release date="2019-09-26" version="0.13.0">
            <description>
                <ul>
                    <li>Using Flatpak and Flathub to distribute the application</li>
                    <li>Using meson as build system</li>
